      • getExitArcsName

        public String getExitArcsName()
        If this is either a node token event for either ExecutionEventType.NODE_TOKEN_SKIPPED or ExecutionEventType.NODE_TOKEN_COMPLETED, this will return the name of the arc (or arcs) on which execution will be proceeding. If execution proceeded on multiple arcs with different labels, this will return the first label.
        Returns:
        The arc name on which execution will proceed if this event is related to a node token skipped or node token completing event.

      • getExitArcsNames

        Returns:
        The arc names on which execution will proceed if this event is related to a node token skipped or node token completing event.
